scene.message:
Nanjo: As expected, there are{nl}
few here who'd make good{nl}
company for Sonomura.{waitkey}{clearbox}Little wonder she's in no{nl}
mood to leave her room...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Sonomura's room is the{nl}
second one straight ahead{nl}
from here.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Coming to visit was{nl}
the right call. Sonomura's{nl}
sure to be glad.{waitkey}{ret}

Patient: There's a girl about{nl}
high-school age on my floor,{nl}
you see...{waitkey}{clearbox}Now and then, I hear the{nl}
voice of a little girl coming{nl}
from there.{waitkey}{clearbox}It's supposed to be a private{nl}
room, so maybe a little{nl}
sister's visiting?{waitkey}{ret}
